  <body style="font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; margin: 0; background: #f8fafc; color: #222;">
    <main style="max-width: 600px; margin: 3rem auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 2px 16px #0001; padding: 2.5rem 2rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: #2d6a4f;">Oak Park Library Tutors</h1>
      <h2 style="font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #555;">In-person K-12 Tutoring at the Oak Park Public Library</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Hi! I'm a local cyber professional with a passion for helping kids succeed. I have experience tutoring and coaching students of all ages and backgrounds. If your child needs support in any K-12 subject, I'm here to helpâ€”right at the Oak Park Public Library.</p>
      <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
